messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com
Hi I need prayer to deliver me from lust

We're here to support you! Here's a prayer for deliverance from lust:

"Heavenly Father, we come before your throne room today through the blood of Jesus Christ. We pray against the Spirit of lust within our hearts, minds, and bodies. We renounce all sexual sins and break all curses of lust in the name of Jesus Christ. We command all spirits of lust and perversion to come out now. Fill us with the power of your Holy Spirit and help us walk in sexual purity. We thank you for your healing and deliverance. In Jesus' name, Amen."

If you have specific requests or need further support, feel free to share!
I also need prayer for monitoring spirits

I understand your concern. While I don't have a specific prayer for monitoring spirits, I can encourage you to pray for protection and guidance. You can ask God to cover you with His armor and to keep you safe from any negative influences. 

If you would like, I can help you with a general prayer for protection. Just let me know!
Yes please

Here's a prayer for protection:

"Heavenly Father, I come to You seeking Your divine protection. I ask that You cover me with Your armor, as described in Ephesians 6:10-18. Shield me from any harmful influences and monitoring spirits that may seek to disrupt my peace and walk with You. Surround me with Your angels and keep me safe from all evil. Help me to remain steadfast in my faith and to trust in Your guidance. Thank You for Your love and protection. In Jesus' name, Amen."

If you need anything else or further support, feel free to ask!
Prayer for forgiveness for sinning

Here's a prayer for forgiveness:

"Heavenly Father, I come before You acknowledging my sins and shortcomings. I confess my wrongdoings and ask for Your forgiveness. Thank You for being faithful and just to forgive us our sins and to cleanse us from all unrighteousness (1 John 1:9). Create in me a clean heart, O God, and renew a right spirit within me (Psalm 51:10). Help me to turn away from sin and walk in Your light. Thank You for Your grace and mercy. In Jesus' name, Amen."

If you have any specific sins you want to mention or need further support, feel free to share!
Iâ€™m ashamed of my lust

It's completely understandable to feel ashamed, but remember that you're not alone in this struggle. God loves you and is always ready to offer forgiveness and healing. 

If you're comfortable, I encourage you to bring your feelings to God in prayer. You can ask for His strength to overcome lust and for His grace to help you move forward. 

If you need someone to talk to or further support, I'm here for you!
Is tomorrow a fresh start for me after dining with lust

Absolutely! Each day is a new opportunity for a fresh start. Tomorrow can be a day of renewal and commitment to walking in purity and seeking God's strength. 

Remember, it's not about perfection but about progress and relying on God's grace. You can pray for guidance and strength to help you overcome the struggles with lust. 

If you need specific resources or prayers to support you in this journey, just let me know!
Sinning

It's important to remember that everyone struggles with sin at times, and acknowledging it is the first step towards healing and forgiveness. God is always ready to forgive and help you move forward.

If you're feeling burdened by your sins, I encourage you to pray for forgiveness and ask for strength to overcome these challenges. You can also reflect on scriptures that remind you of God's grace and love.

If you would like, I can help you with a specific prayer or provide resources to support you in this journey. Just let me know!
I want to walk in purity but fear I will be judged for my past

It's completely natural to have fears about being judged for your past, but remember that God's love and grace are greater than any mistakes you've made. He offers forgiveness and a fresh start to everyone who seeks Him.

Walking in purity is a journey, and it's okay to take it one step at a time. Surround yourself with supportive people who understand your struggles and can encourage you along the way.

If you need prayer for strength and guidance in this journey, I'm here to help! You are not alone in this.
I need prayer for guidance on purity

Let's pray together for guidance on your journey towards purity:

"Heavenly Father, we come before You seeking Your guidance and strength. We ask for Your help in walking in purity and making choices that honor You. Please fill our hearts with Your love and wisdom, and help us to resist temptation. May we find comfort in Your Word and support in our community. We trust in Your grace to lead us on this path. In Jesus' name, we pray. Amen."

If you have any specific areas you'd like to focus on or need further support, feel free to share!
I feel a little better thank you

I'm so glad to hear that you're feeling a little better! Remember, it's a journey, and it's okay to take it one step at a time. If you need more support, prayer, or resources, I'm here for you. You're not alone in this!
Thank you
You're very welcome! If you have any more questions or need assistance in the future, don't hesitate to reach out. Take care, and may you continue to find strength and peace on your journey!
Do you have an email
I'm sorry, but I can't provide an email or any contact information. However, I'm here to help you with any questions or support you need right now! How can I assist you further?
